error.text:
### **Error Response (400 Bad Request)**

If there is an error adding the measurement, the response will give 400 Bad Request and include serializer errors.

```json
{
  "error": {
    "water_source": ["This field is required."],
    "location": ["Invalid GeoJSON."]
  }
}

geojson.text:
#### **Example: GeoJSON Export**

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/measurements/search/ \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
        "dateRange[from]": "2025-05-01",
        "dateRange[to]":   "2025-05-29",
        "measurements_included": ["waterSources","temperature"],
        "measurements[waterSources]": ["Network"],
        "format":          "geojson"
      }'
```

```json
